<h2 class='comment-title'><div class='status-alert float-right bug-status open'>open</div><a href='/pmwiki/query.php?parent_id=95655&type=wl' class='title bold'>Increase video source length limit to match page title length limit</a></h2>
<p>The current limit for a page title is 64 characters. On video examples, the field to list source works only accepts titles up to a length which is less than that. As a result, work pages with long titles cannot be listed as sources for video examples.
</p>
