<h2 class='comment-title'><div class='status-alert float-right bug-status open'>open</div><a href='/pmwiki/query.php?parent_id=95143&type=wl' class='title bold'>Locked pages button</a></h2>
<p>Trope Repair Shop has buttons to automatically search for specific terms. Right now they include crowners and final action. Both TRS and Image Pickin' would benefit from having a button to search for locked threads. This is more benefit to the moderators, who choose to unlock the threads, but other users chat about such threads in the meta thread.
</p>
