<p><a class='twikilink' href='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ExactlyWhatItSaysOnTheTin' title='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ExactlyWhatItSaysOnTheTin'>Exactly What It Says on the Tin</a>. It would make pages heavy on notes, such as the <a class='twikilink' href='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MemeticMutation' title='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MemeticMutation'>Memetic Mutation</a> subpages and <a class='twikilink' href='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/JustForFun/TropeEpitaph' title='/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/JustForFun/TropeEpitaph'>Trope Epitaph</a>, much easier to read.
