<h2 class='comment-title'><div class='status-alert float-right bug-status open'>open</div><a href='/pmwiki/query.php?parent_id=94661&type=wl' class='title bold'>Better history record for TLP drafts</a></h2>
<p>So I just restored a rogue-discarded draft. However, after I did so I realized that the troper who discarded it lacks any sort of edit history whatsoever. This makes me a bit concerned I may have gotten their username slightly misspelled but I can't check now that it was restored.
</p><p>A proper log on the history of launch and discard record would be super helpful, especially to track rogue-discards and rogue-launches. If the draft is sent back to the normal TLP page after being launched or discarded, having a way to keep a record of what happened would be great.
</p>
<span class="edited-by">Edited by WarJay77</span>
