<h2 class='comment-title'><div class='status-alert float-right bug-status open'>open</div><a href='/pmwiki/query.php?parent_id=80221&type=wl' class='title bold'>Add a confirmation to &quot;Mark All As Read&quot; on the Following page</a></h2>
<p>I've misclicked "Mark All As Read" on my Following page several times, causing me to be unable to know whose edits I already seen. The button on the forum has a confirmation prompt, therefore I think the Following page's button should have it added as well as I don't want to worry about this happening and others may have the same problem. Thank you.
</p>
