<h2 class='comment-title'><div class='status-alert float-right bug-status open'>open</div><a href='/pmwiki/query.php?parent_id=93952&type=wl' class='title bold'>One Clip - Many Tropes</a></h2>
<p>I wish for the ability to attach video examples to <em>multiple</em> relevant tropes instead of only one.
</p><p>It would not only make the process of uploading and adding examples simpler and more efficient, it also would also avoid the works pages from getting cluttered with duplicate clips, which users would be forced to upload for every displayed trope individually.
</p>
